#. <section class="sutta" id="an5.273"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an5.273-285:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 5"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 5"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an5.273-285:0.2"
msgid "27. Sammutipeyyāla"
msgstr "27. Abbreviated Texts on Appointments"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "an5.273-285:0.3"
msgid "273–285. Senāsanapaññāpakasuttādi"
msgstr "273–285. A Lodgings Assigner"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an5.273-285:1.1"
msgid "“Pañcahi, bhikkhave, dhammehi samannāgato senāsanapaññāpako na sammannitabbo … pe … paññattāpaññattaṃ na jānāti … pe … senāsanapaññāpako sammannitabbo … pe … paññattāpaññattaṃ jānāti … pe …."
msgstr "“Mendicants, a person with five qualities should not be appointed as lodgings assigner … they don’t know if a lodging has been assigned or not … A person with five qualities should be appointed as lodgings assigner … they know if a lodging has been assigned or not …"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
#. VAR: pe … gahitāgahitaṃ → paññattāpaññattaṃ (bj, s1-3, km)
#. VAR: pe … gahitāgahitaṃ → paññattāpaññattaṃ (bj, s1-3, km)
msgctxt "an5.273-285:2.1"
msgid "Senāsanagāhāpako na sammannitabbo … pe … gahitāgahitaṃ na jānāti … pe … senāsanagāhāpako sammannitabbo … pe … gahitāgahitaṃ jānāti … pe …."
msgstr "A person should not be appointed as lodgings allocator … they don’t know if a lodging has been allocated or not … A person should be appointed as lodgings allocator … they know if a lodging has been allocated or not …"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "an5.273-285:3.1"
msgid "Bhaṇḍāgāriko na sammannitabbo … pe … guttāguttaṃ na jānāti … bhaṇḍāgāriko sammannitabbo … pe … guttāguttaṃ jānāti …."
msgstr "A person should not be appointed as storeperson … they don’t know if stores are protected or not … A person should be appointed as storeperson … they know if stores are protected or not …"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli3.275"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "an5.273-285:4.1"
msgid "Cīvarapaṭiggāhako na sammannitabbo … pe … gahitāgahitaṃ na jānāti … cīvarapaṭiggāhako sammannitabbo … pe … gahitāgahitaṃ jānāti …."
msgstr "… robe receiver …"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "an5.273-285:5.1"
msgid "Cīvarabhājako na sammannitabbo … pe … bhājitābhājitaṃ na jānāti … cīvarabhājako sammannitabbo … pe … bhājitābhājitaṃ jānāti …."
msgstr "… robe distributor …"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc6"></a>
msgctxt "an5.273-285:6.1"
msgid "Yāgubhājako na sammannitabbo … pe … yāgubhājako sammannitabbo … pe …."
msgstr "… porridge distributor …"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc7"></a>
msgctxt "an5.273-285:7.1"
msgid "Phalabhājako na sammannitabbo … pe … phalabhājako sammannitabbo … pe …."
msgstr "… fruit distributor …"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc8"></a>
msgctxt "an5.273-285:8.1"
msgid "Khajjakabhājako na sammannitabbo … pe … bhājitābhājitaṃ na jānāti … khajjakabhājako sammannitabbo … pe … bhājitābhājitaṃ jānāti …."
msgstr "… cake distributor …"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc9"></a>
msgctxt "an5.273-285:9.1"
msgid "Appamattakavissajjako na sammannitabbo … pe … vissajjitāvissajjitaṃ na jānāti … appamattakavissajjako sammannitabbo … pe … vissajjitāvissajjitaṃ jānāti …."
msgstr "… dispenser of minor accessories …"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc10"></a>
msgctxt "an5.273-285:10.1"
msgid "Sāṭiyaggāhāpako na sammannitabbo … pe … gahitāgahitaṃ na jānāti … sāṭiyaggāhāpako sammannitabbo … pe … gahitāgahitaṃ jānāti …."
msgstr "… allocator of bathing cloths …"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc11"></a>
msgctxt "an5.273-285:11.1"
msgid "Pattaggāhāpako na sammannitabbo … pe … gahitāgahitaṃ na jānāti … pattaggāhāpako sammannitabbo … pe … gahitāgahitaṃ jānāti …."
msgstr "… bowl allocator …"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc12"></a>
msgctxt "an5.273-285:12.1"
msgid "Ārāmikapesako na sammannitabbo … pe … ārāmikapesako sammannitabbo … pe …."
msgstr "… supervisor of monastery staff …"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc13"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc14"></a>
msgctxt "an5.273-285:13.1"
msgid "Sāmaṇerapesako na sammannitabbo … pe … sāmaṇerapesako sammannitabbo … pe …. Sammato na pesetabbo … pe … sammato pesetabbo … pe …."
msgstr "… supervisor of novices …"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc15"></a>
msgctxt "an5.273-285:15.1"
msgid "Sāmaṇerapesako bālo veditabbo … pe … paṇḍito veditabbo … khataṃ upahataṃ attānaṃ pariharati … akkhataṃ anupahataṃ attānaṃ pariharati … yathābhataṃ nikkhitto evaṃ niraye … yathābhataṃ nikkhitto evaṃ sagge."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an5.273-285:15.2"
msgid "Katamehi pañcahi?"
msgstr "What five?"

msgctxt "an5.273-285:15.3"
msgid "Na chandāgatiṃ gacchati, na dosāgatiṃ gacchati, na mohāgatiṃ gacchati, na bhayāgatiṃ gacchati, pesitāpesitaṃ jānāti."
msgstr "They don’t make decisions prejudiced by favoritism, hostility, stupidity, and cowardice. And they know if a novice has been supervised or not."

msgctxt "an5.273-285:15.4"
msgid "Imehi kho, bhikkhave, pañcahi dhammehi samannāgato sāmaṇerapesako yathābhataṃ nikkhitto evaṃ sagge”ti."
msgstr "A supervisor of novices with these five qualities is raised up to heaven.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an5.273-285:15.5"
msgid "Cuddasamaṃ."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an5.273-285:15.6"
msgid "Sammutipeyyālaṃ niṭṭhitaṃ."
msgstr ""
